3. Personal Portfolio Layout (HTML + CSS Explanation)

Structure Suggestion:
Use HTML5 layout: <header>, <nav>, <main>, <footer>
Apply CSS Grid or Flexbox for layout.

Example:
html

<header>My Portfolio</header>
<nav>Home | Projects | Contact</nav>
<main>Showcase Projects Here</main>
<footer>&copy; 2025 My Name</footer>
CSS Brief:

css

body { font-family: Arial; margin: 0; }
header, nav, footer { background: #333; color: white; padding: 10px; }
main { padding: 20px; }
